org.jamwiki.db

Class SybaseASAQueryHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jamwiki.db.AnsiQueryHandler
      • org.jamwiki.db.SybaseASAQueryHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    QueryHandler

    public class SybaseASAQueryHandler
extends AnsiQueryHandler
    Sybase ASA-specific implementation of the QueryHandler interface. This class implements specific methods for instances where Sybase ASA does not support the default ANSI SQL syntax.
